# built-in lockfile-based dep install — wire up whatever your project needs
# (compose up, db seed, env scaffolding, etc.).
# Cwd:  the new worktree.
# Env:  GWT_MAIN (main repo root), GWT_WT (this worktree path).
# Logs: <worktree>/.gwt-postcreate.log (stdout + stderr).
